BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Davis Downtown": "https://davisdowntown.com/event/davis-farmers-market-year-round-fresh-local-in-central-park-50th-anniversary-year/2026-03-11/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:davis_downtown
SUMMARY:Davis Farmers Market – Year-Round Fresh & Local in Central Park 
 (50th Anniversary Year!)
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260311T150000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260311T180000
UID:10000234-1773241200-1773252000@davisdowntown.com
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate 50 years of community and bounty at the Davis Farmer
 s Market in 2026! This iconic\, award-winning market is the heartbeat of D
 avis – bringing together local farmers\, artisans\, bakers\, food vendor
 s\, and makers every week. \n\nWednesdays: 3:00 PM – 6:00 PM (September
 –March)\; 4:00 PM – 8:00 PM Picnic in the Park with live music (April
 –August)\n\nShop the freshest seasonal produce\, farm-fresh eggs/meats/c
 heese\, artisan crafts\, hot prepared foods\, coffee\, baked goods\, and m
 ore! All grown or made right here in our region. Enjoy live music (especia
 lly during summer Picnic in the Park Wednesdays)\, family activities\, SNA
 P matching programs\, and the lively downtown energy that makes it a favor
 ite gathering spot for residents\, UC Davis students\, families\, and visi
 tors. \nFree entry – bring your bags and support local agriculture\, sus
 tainability\, and small businesses! Rain or shine\, it’s always a great 
 day out. \nSpecial 2026 highlights: 50th anniversary celebrations througho
 ut the year. Don’t miss the big community event on August 1!
LOCATION:Central Park\, 301 C St.\, Davis\, CA\, 95616\, United States
URL:https://davisdowntown.com/event/davis-farmers-market-year-round-fresh-
 local-in-central-park-50th-anniversary-year/2026-03-11/
X-SOURCE:Davis Downtown
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Meetup Yolo County Board Game Gathering": "https://www.meetup.com/yolo-county-board-game-gathering/events/313439628/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:meetup_yolo_county_board_game_gathering
X-SOURCE:Meetup Yolo County Board Game Gathering
UID:event_313439628@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260311T022922Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260311T170000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260311T210000
SUMMARY:Weekly Game Night at Blue Note
DESCRIPTION:Yolo County Board Game Gathering\nUpdate 8/14/25:\n**We're sti
 ll active**\, but we primarily use Discord to chat and plan events. (See g
 roup description for invite link.)\n\nWe still meet every Wednesday for bo
 ard games at Blue Note Brewing Company. We'll have a handful of tables res
 erved near the back\; just look for the pile of board games.\n\nPeople usu
 ally start arriving around 5pm\, and games start whenever people are ready
 . Blue Note closes at 9pm\, and although we have a 5-10 minute grace perio
 d there\, you should be in the process of final scoring by 9\, or else pac
 k it up and play again another day.\n\nGame night is open to all ages! Blu
 e Note is a brewery\, not a bar\, so there's no restriction against minors
 . In addition to their crafted-in-house beer selection\, water and sodas a
 re available.\n\nYou're not required to buy anything in order to join us\,
  but we do encourage you to support local businesses. Blue Note's chef tea
 m makes a mean pizza\, and there are other nearby downtown restaurants and
  businesses.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/yolo-county-board-game-gathering/even
 ts/313439628/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260220T021418Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260220T021418Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
