DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260313T100000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260313T114500
SUMMARY:Healing Arts 6-Session Workshop
DESCRIPTION:Pence Adult Art Programs\nThe Pence’s 6-session Healing Arts
  workshop uses art as a healing language for those experiencing grief from
  the loss of a loved one. Through the process of art making\, participants
  will have opportunities for discussion\, education\, and connecting with 
 peers in a safe and supportive space in the Pence Learning Center under th
 e guidance of facilitators Amy Vidra and Lyndsey Rocca.\n\nREGISTRATION ON
 LINE IS REQUIRED IN ADVANCE through the Pence Gallery's website\, and spac
 e is limited to the first 8 participants who register. Participants must b
 e 18 or older\, and no art experience is necessary. This program is genero
 usly sponsored by Bob & Joanne Andresen.\n\nHealing Arts 6-Session Worksho
 p\nFridays\\\, 10\\-11:45 AM \\| Mar\\. 13\\\, 20\\\, 27 & Apr\\. 3\\\, 10
 \\\, 17\n$25 Members\, $35 Non-Members (all materials included)\n\n**Remin
 der - an RSVP on Meetup does NOT count as registration. Registration is re
 quired in advance through the [Pence’s website](https://pencegallery.org
 /education/programs/workshops-and-classes/).**\n\nPlease note that when re
 gistering for this program\, you are signing up for all 6 sessions. If you
  are unable to attend one or more of the sessions\, please let us know in 
 advance.\n\nAny questions? Email pencegallery@gmail.com
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/pence-adult-art-programs/events/31306
 9204/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260126T200432Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260126T200432Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
