SUMMARY:Sip Yolo with Yolo County Wines
DESCRIPTION:Discover the charm of Yolo County’s wine country this season by visiting our Yolo Wines wineries. From cozy tasting rooms to stunning vineyard views\, each tasting room offers award-winning wines\, hometown hospitality\, and wines perfect for gifting.  Gather your friends\, sip something new\, and make this season a little more delicious. \nVisit https://www.yolocountywines.com/events to see holiday winery events and to plan your wine trail! \n@berryessagapvineyards @collinadebella @elevationten @fjordoakwinery @greatbearvineyards @grindstonewines @heringerestates @juliettawinery @matchbookwines @sekahills @siltwineco @taberranch @turkovichwines  \n 
URL:https://visityolo.com/event/sip-yolo-with-yolo-county-wines/2026-03-13/
LOCATION:Yolo County Vineyard and Winery Association\, 13 winery locations!
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visityolo.com/wp-content/uploads/yolo-county-wines.jpeg
END:VEVENT
