UID:10002813-1773514800-1773522000@visitdavis.org
SUMMARY:Renegade Orchestra at Veterans Memorial Theater in Davis
DESCRIPTION:Renegade Orchestra is the bay area’s rock and roll orchestra! \n“The Beauty of a Symphony\, the Soul of a Rock Band” \nClap your hands\, tap your feet\, and yell all you want – the Renegade Orchestra embraces the virtuosic skills of top bay area musicians and turns them loose on songs orchestras have never or maybe shouldn’t do.  \n“Classical Rebels.” The Bohemian \n“The Renegade Orchestra would rather tackle Hendrix than Handel.” Mercury News \nFor this concert\, the Renegade Orchestra will be performing a set of music called “Sounds of San Francisco” – all fun classic songs from Jefferson Airplane’s Somebody to Love\, It’s a Beautiful Day’s White Bird\, and even some orchestral punk by the Dead Kennedys. 
URL:https://visitdavis.org/event/renegade-orchestra-at-veterans-memorial-theater-in-davis/
LOCATION:Davis Veterans Memorial Theater\, 277 E. 14th Street\, Davis CA\, Davis\, 95616\, United States
END:VEVENT
