UID:b2cdc679b2052615144ea0654fb1f01b@events.yolocountylibrary.org
DESCRIPTION:Nowruz\, the Persian New Year\, is celebrated across many Pers
 ianate societies and welcomes the arrival of spring and the vernal equinox
 ! Join us in celebrating Nowruz with lively Persian music\, poetry readin
 g\, fun crafts\, storytime and much more!
LOCATION:Blanchard Room\, Small Conference Room\, Mary L Stephens Davis Br
 anch Library
