SUMMARY:Stephen Sosnick Memorial Chess Festival
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260411T020000Z
DTEND;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260413T030000Z
UID:3784f8a031e5d0087fb40a6b1dc6a4d78192025_9:17:24_PM@campusgroups.com
DESCRIPTION:The Chess Club at UC Davis and Sosnick Chess\, a non-profit ho
 noring the late UCD Professor Stephen Sosnick\, join forces to sponsor a w
 eekend chess festival on April 10-12\, 2026 at the UCD Conference Center. 
 Grand Master Joel Benjaman will play a 25-person simultaneous exhibition g
 ame\, lecture and provide game commentary to festival attendees. There is 
 no charge to attend the festival. On each of Saturday and Sunday there wil
 l also be a US Chess Federation sanctioned tournament where Unrated player
 s to International Masters test their skills in one of the several levels 
 of tournament play. All ages are welcome. Sign up to play in the tournamen
 t is through https://www.kingregistration.com/tournaments#davis.
LOCATION:UC Davis Confrence Center\, 1 Shields Ave\, Davis\, California 95
 616\, United States
