DESCRIPTION:The Annual Collegiate Wushu Tournament was created to foster a
 nd promote collegiate-level wushu nationwide. The event brings together st
 udent-athletes from universities nationwide to compete\, connect\, and cel
 ebrate the discipline\, athleticism\, and cultural heritage of wushu. Thro
 ugh Taolu competition\, the tournament provides a platform for skill devel
 opment\, sportsmanship\, and the continued growth of wushu within collegia
 te communities.
URL:https://aggielife.ucdavis.edu/rsvp?id=907778
X-SOURCE:UC Davis CampusGroups
END:VEVENT
